description: The E.P.L Match Day skill will keep you up to date on scheduled fixtures, results for matches for the current day which have concluded and live scores if the match is currently in progress.
exampleInteractions: Alexa ask E.P.L Match Day for the matches
Get me the matches for today
name: E.P.L Matchday
shortDescription: The E.P.L Match Day skill will provide schedules and live scores for all English Premier League football fixtures
